        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 17. Sporadopora dichotoma. (a) Branch cross section displaying ampullae cavities and gastro- and dactylopore tubes. (b) Branch longitudinal section displaying curvature of gastro- and dactylopore tubes. (c) Ampulla with efferent duct (left side) and gastropore tube (centre). (d) Gastrostyle. (e) Coenosteal texture and gastro- and dactylopores. (f) Efferent pore seen from interior of ampulla." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4751315/files/figure.png" .

